      • getObfuscatedPassword

        @Nullable
public String getObfuscatedPassword()
        Returns the password in obfuscated fashion which means everything except the first and last character replaced by stars. If the password is one or two characters long we'll obfuscate it entirely.
        返回:
        the obfuscated password
